数据路连接数：
mysql> SHOW STATUS LIKE 'Threads%';
+-------------------+-------+
| Variable_name     | Value |
+-------------------+-------+
| Threads_cached    | 2     |
| Threads_connected | 3     |
| Threads_created   | 5     |
| Threads_running   | 2     |
+-------------------+-------+
4 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql>
mysql> SHOW GLOBAL STATUS LIKE 'Thread%';
+-------------------+-------+
| Variable_name     | Value |
+-------------------+-------+
| Threads_cached    | 2     |
| Threads_connected | 3     |
| Threads_created   | 5     |
| Threads_running   | 2     |
+-------------------+-------+
4 rows in set (0.01 sec)


系统设置最大连接数：
mysql> SHOW VARIABLES LIKE '%max_connections%';
+------------------------+-------+
| Variable_name          | Value |
+------------------------+-------+
| max_connections        | 151   |
| mysqlx_max_connections | 100   |
+------------------------+-------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)


